
Iteration:yenileme
In this lesson we are going to learn how variables can be used to store values and execute our code with specific data.
(Bu derste, değerleri depolamak ve kodumuzu belirli verilerle yürütmek için değişkenlerin nasıl kullanılabileceğini öğreneceğiz.)

For loops Refresher:
For loops allow us to repeat code a specific amount ot times.

When you run this code you will get a square shape.

Each side of the square will be 50px.


i is changing its value on every iteration(yenileme).

Each time the loop runs, the i value will increase one by one.


The initial value of i is 0.

When the value of i is 4, the loop ends.
